50:20.085 --> 50:22.487
-(groans)
-No. No one outside of this room

50:22.620 --> 50:24.021
can know what's happening.

50:24.155 --> 50:25.856
He already knows.
I've called him.

50:25.990 --> 50:28.025
-You told Dad?
-What? You told the father?!

50:28.193 --> 50:29.994
Yes.

50:32.530 --> 50:34.532
(phone ringing)

50:37.602 --> 50:38.469
Hello?

50:38.603 --> 50:39.637
Bernard Lewinsky?

50:39.770 --> 50:41.872
-Yes.
-I'm Mike Emmick with the office

50:42.006 --> 50:43.508
of Independent Counsel
Kenneth Starr.

50:43.641 --> 50:44.975
