and your wife.

50:45.110 --> 50:46.711
-Ex-wife.
-Ex-wife.

50:48.313 --> 50:50.381
Right. Sorry.

50:50.548 --> 50:54.385
Sir, we have evidence sufficient
to prosecute Monica

50:54.552 --> 50:55.920
for multiple felonies.

50:56.053 --> 50:57.555
We're offering her a chance

50:57.688 --> 50:59.924
to cooperate
with our office instead.

51:00.057 --> 51:01.058
Do you understand?

51:01.192 --> 51:03.094
Isn't she entitled
to an attorney?

51:03.228 --> 51:04.195
-An attorney?
-Yes.

51:04.329 --> 51:06.397
Yeah.
Does she have an attorney?

51:07.832 --> 51:09.200
Put Monica on the phone.

51:10.968 --> 51:12.837
He wants to talk to you.

51:20.678 --> 51:21.912
Hi, Daddy.

51:22.079 --> 51:23.581
Monka.

51:23.714 --> 51:26.016
I'm here with Bill Ginsburg.

51:26.151 --> 51:27.585
He's gonna be your attorney.

51:27.752 --> 51:29.854
Your friend Bill?

51:29.987 --> 51:31.756
-The malpractice lawyer?
-Yeah.

51:31.922 --> 51:34.091
I'm, uh...
I'm gonna hand you over.

51:35.059 --> 51:36.394
Do as he says, okay?

51:36.527 --> 51:37.762
Okay.

51:42.167 --> 51:44.435
Did they put you in bracelets,
sweetheart?

51:44.569 --> 51:46.437
Uh, what?

51:46.571 --> 51:48.539
-Are you in custody now, dear?
-Oh.

51:48.673 --> 51:50.107
Um...

51:51.041 --> 51:53.244
No, no.
Well, I don't think so.

51:53.378 --> 51:55.079
They just keep asking me to...
(shudders)

51:55.213 --> 51:56.281
to make a decision.

51:56.414 --> 51:57.748
All right,
put me through to them.

51:57.882 --> 51:59.250
Okay.

51:59.384 --> 52:00.785
He wants to talk to you.

52:04.054 --> 52:05.556
-Hello?
-Name, please.

52:05.690 --> 52:07.825
Who am I talking to?

52:07.958 --> 52:10.328
-Mike Emmick. Who is this?
-This is William Ginsburg.

52:10.461 --> 52:12.497
-I'm Monica's attorney.
-(mouths)

52:12.630 --> 52:13.964
(mouths)

52:14.098 --> 52:15.666
Mr. Ginsburg,

52:15.800 --> 52:18.102
we have been negotiating
with Ms. Lewinsky here

52:18.236 --> 52:19.937
-for 11 hours now...
-Negotiating? Really?

52:20.070 --> 52:23.441
Is that the new term of art
for "unlawful detention"?

52:23.574 --> 52:25.676
Sir, she could have left
at any time.

52:25.810 --> 52:29.146
Shut the fuck up,
you motherfucking cocksucker.

52:30.315 --> 52:32.250
-Excuse me?
-We've already heard

52:32.383 --> 52:33.484
what you want her to do.

52:33.618 --> 52:35.152
Now tell us
what she's gonna get for it.

52:35.286 --> 52:38.289
Full transactional immunity
from prosecution!

52:38.423 --> 52:40.791
-I want that in writing.
-Yeah, well,
it's nearly midnight here.

52:40.925 --> 52:42.760
-We've been down this road
with the mother.
-Too bad,

52:42.893 --> 52:44.362
so sad. Write it up.

52:44.495 --> 52:46.664
-Now.
-We don't have a typewriter
here.

52:46.831 --> 52:48.499
-Then write it out by hand
and fax it.
-No, we don't have

52:48.666 --> 52:51.336
-a fax machine either.
-You know, I know that hotel.

52:51.502 --> 52:53.271
I've stayed at that hotel.
They've got a fax machine.

52:53.404 --> 52:54.439
It's a goddamn

52:54.572 --> 52:55.606
Ritz-Carlton.

52:55.740 --> 52:58.309
Sir, we are
not going to use a communal fax.

52:58.443 --> 53:00.811
You are a lying sack of shit.

53:00.945 --> 53:03.381
Okay, look... I-I am sorry,
but I do not see

53:03.514 --> 53:05.550
the need to use profanity.

53:05.683 --> 53:06.951
That makes one of us.

53:07.084 --> 53:09.019
Because the plain fact
of the matter is

53:09.153 --> 53:11.556
you don't have the power
to put a single goddamn thing

53:11.689 --> 53:13.291
in writing now, do you?

53:13.424 --> 53:15.693
Fucking hang up on this prick.

53:15.860 --> 53:17.728
Mr. Ginsburg...
(exhales)

53:17.862 --> 53:19.464
this is a real offer.

53:19.597 --> 53:21.832
Tomorrow, we will fax it to you.

53:21.966 --> 53:23.501
You will have it in writing.

53:23.634 --> 53:24.702
So, for Monica's sake,

53:24.869 --> 53:26.671
for her future,

53:26.804 --> 53:27.838
believe me when I say
you do not want...

53:27.972 --> 53:28.839
Put my client back

53:28.973 --> 53:30.007
on the phone.

53:40.285 --> 53:41.552
What's going on?

53:41.686 --> 53:43.721
Sweetheart, I want you to listen
very carefully.

53:43.854 --> 53:45.222
Do exactly as I say.

53:45.356 --> 53:46.557
Stand up,

53:46.691 --> 53:47.858
don't say a word,

53:47.992 --> 53:50.395
walk out the door.

53:50.528 --> 53:51.896
What?

53:52.062 --> 53:54.399
They should never have held you
there, and they know it.

53:54.532 --> 53:56.401
Now go get your mother
and go home.

53:56.567 --> 53:57.402
Monica,

53:57.568 --> 53:58.903
nothing's gonna happen.

54:00.638 --> 54:03.040
(whispers): They said
they were gonna send me to jail.

54:03.173 --> 54:04.275
If they wanted to arrest you,

54:04.409 --> 54:05.443
they would have
done that already.

54:05.576 --> 54:06.877
I'm gonna hop on a red-eye.

54:07.011 --> 54:08.513
I'll see you in the morning.

54:08.646 --> 54:10.415
Now please go.

54:10.548 --> 54:12.182
I swear to you on my life,

54:12.317 --> 54:14.051
they cannot stop you.

54:15.420 --> 54:18.088
Monica, do you understand?

54:19.890 --> 54:21.258
Yes.

54:22.760 --> 54:24.462
(line clicks)

54:24.595 --> 54:25.930
(exhales)

54:26.096 --> 54:27.097
(sniffles)

54:29.934 --> 54:32.102
Mom, get your coat.
We're leaving.

54:34.605 --> 54:36.240
BENNETT:
There it is.

54:36.374 --> 54:37.775
Nice work.

54:42.580 --> 54:43.614
(door opens)

54:43.781 --> 54:45.282
So this is your final decision?

54:49.420 --> 54:50.755
Yes.

54:54.392 --> 54:56.461
Uh, thank you...

54:56.627 --> 54:59.797
uh, so much for everything.

55:01.466 --> 55:03.133
Good night, Monica.

55:03.267 --> 55:05.202
Good night.

55:08.606 --> 55:10.641
(breathing heavily)

55:14.812 --> 55:17.982
* *

