56:01.859 --> 56:04.028
-(clinking)
-(cabinet door creaks)

56:04.194 --> 56:05.863
We could go to Canada.

56:07.432 --> 56:08.866
Tonight.

56:11.469 --> 56:13.838
We just get in the Jeep
and drive.

56:15.205 --> 56:17.842
Honey, they would
stop us at the border.

56:17.975 --> 56:19.677
They're the government.

56:19.810 --> 56:23.047
All you need to do now
is just get some sleep, and...

56:23.213 --> 56:25.149
-we will finish this tomorrow.
-I just...

56:25.282 --> 56:26.551
If I don't call Betty...

56:26.684 --> 56:28.052
No!

56:29.053 --> 56:30.087
You can't.

56:30.220 --> 56:32.557
You cannot!

56:32.723 --> 56:36.326
You have to look out
for your own life now, honey,

56:36.461 --> 56:38.463
