56:41.165 --> 56:43.167
(shuddering softly)

56:45.235 --> 56:47.237
I'm gonna take a shower.

56:48.739 --> 56:50.407
Okay.
All right.

56:50.575 --> 56:52.677
-I'm sorry.
-I don't want...

57:07.758 --> 57:09.760
* *

